full_text: My people SUFFERING gahLEE. It never ends. https://t.co/vO2hODWyAA
You easily find and create purpose within yourself. Just simply facing and organizing your current reality.

It's very obvious when people just make conversation to fill space. I particularly notice when people are quick to try to interrupt before I finish completing and expressing a thought. It comes across as hollow and superficial; very boring.
